A punk and a nun are on the bus. Punk turns to a nun:
- Nun, I want you in the most perverted form!
The nun blushed and got off the bus at the nearest stop. The bus driver says to the punk:
- Hey punk, I know how to help you. Every Wednesday, this nun comes to pray at the chapel in the cemetery. You pretend to be God, but there's a situation.
Wednesday. The punk put on a cape with a hood, came to the cemetery and hid behind the chapel. A nun came to the chapel and prayed. And the punk tells her in a frantic voice:
- I am your God, you must give yourself to me right now!
Nun:
- God willing, but I want to keep my virginity, let it be anal sex.
After rough anal sex, the punk takes off his hood and screams joyfully:
- Deceived, deceived! I'm that punk from the bus!
The nun takes off her hood:
- And I'm the driver of that bus!
